    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80b2-aeff-ec1d29bc455b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A pilot test was done on freshmen students with 3 characteristics: knowledge level, demographics and motivation. Results show computational feasibility of the approach. Authors argue for large-scale studies. ",
